 filename←##.Laguntza.BuildDocFromAllPages ref
 html←↑F.NGET filename
 noOf←0 ⍝ There is no application of italic ...
 noOf+←2×+/html∘{+/⍵⍷⍺}'Invalid link'
 noOf+←2×+/html∘{+/⍵⍷⍺}'Ambiguous link'
 has←+/¨html∘{+/⍵⍷⍺}¨'<em>' '</em>'
 →T.GoToTidyUp≠/has
 →T.GoToTidyUp noOf≠+/has
 has←+/¨html∘{+/⍵⍷⍺}¨'<strong>' '</strong>'
 →T.GoToTidyUp≠/has
 →T.GoToTidyUp noOf≠+/has

 R←T._OK
∆TidyUp:
